<TEXTAREA NAME="EditedMessage" ROWS=10 COLS=45 WRAP="VIRTUAL">Wow such a Change of topics...from cheating to role-playing.

Does anyone remember the Mud’s? Such as Medievia, the Realm, Dagger Fall, Baldurs Gate and some others. Those had role-play value, there were no 3|337 DooDz or whatever the hell you call them. Just solid role-playing, no Evil race EVER hooked up with a Good saintly race!

But my thought still stands about EQ; it’s no longer about role-playing. It’s about gaining the better item a never ending "one-upmanship."

StaticEnzo, Really...stop blaming other ppl, if your going to blame other ppl blame the 80,000 that joined after the first 3 servers started! With every new addition to the game whining and bitching increases. And as I said ppl always want the biggest and best thing for themselves so cheating WILL increase over the course of the game. Also about you kicking my ass over ruining your experience playing Tabletop at some RP store like wizards or something. I'd have YOUR ass slapped with a lawsuit so fast you'd never play a RP game again! Yes, you can report me I could care less I'll find you and harass you online EVERY time I find you! BLAH So THERE NEENER NEENER NE NEER!! (Yes, that was meant to sound VERY childish) People will ALWAYS want cheats! And ppl will always HATE cheats!! Get over it man. Things will NEVER be the same and there is NOTHING you can do to change it, nothing ANYONE can do! Not even Verant. They can try but in the end what is really needed is a revamp of the game to keep ppl from wanting to cheat, but after the pizazz (sp?) wears off everyone will want the cheats! Kinda sux doesn't it, which’s life live with it. U can have all the brains, all the muscle, EVERYTHING but you still can't change it!

BTW about there not being any danger in the CC. That’s a Load, there was always danger in the spot. If a mob popped on the ledge u were screwed, he would quad hit for 80's and bash for about 50. Yes, I died to him about 30 times total! It’s the price you pay!

Some one stated Diablo as being a hack fest, YES, it is! BUT the hacks take it off the dusty shelves to be played again! I am NOT saying that I agree with it! I am saying it adds replay value to it!

D23, LoL try RPing a Paladin named Jhoan De’arco (Joan of arc), LoL you get VERY interesting tells while on! And about the Buffs, heh heh that’s pushing it. I would be amazed if anyone actually gets a buff from you!

ShiroKenshi, That’s fine. But you, being as smart as you are should know that the RP value in EQ is shot! I hope to see the New RP server they are setting up! Maybe a breath of fresh air! LoL and many times I am CONSTANTLY holding two steins, Hey I am the master brewer/drunkard heh heh.

About the Cheating I said before that I Report the bug when I find it (I.e. the dalnir thing I posted). If they don’t fix it within like a month I Exploit it! I told them it was there, its in their ball field now! Now MAYBE it wasn’t a bug and maybe they MENT for that place to be there I DON’T KNOW!!

Well That’s about it for now, my opinion on this has not changed yet! GIVE ME SOMETHING to TRY and swaver me!
